# Offline Desktop BI currently does not require any mandatory runtime environment
# variables for local development. This file exists to satisfy the repository
# baseline documented in AGENT.md and to provide a stable place for future
# optional overrides.

# Example future overrides:
# OFFLINE_BI_LOG_LEVEL=info
# OFFLINE_BI_WORKSPACE_DIR=E:\offline-bi-workspace
# OFFLINE_BI_TELEMETRY_METRICS=true
# OFFLINE_BI_TELEMETRY_DEBUG=false
